      "para_id": "Q001102.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) For Nanše of the Šeše-ĝara , En-metena , ruler of Lagaš , chosen by Nanše in the heart , chief governor of Ninĝirsu , chosen brother of Nindara , the mighty master , child of En-ana-tum , ruler of Lagaš , fashioned a door of white cedar , and installed it in the temple for his well-being ."
    }
  ],
